des: My Health allows user to see different list of options they can try out to improve their mood and life during this pandemic. Some people are struggling and My Health has easy and helpful suggestion that can help. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number
